{"name":"SPACER","type":"npc_template","img":"systems/lancer/assets/icons/npc_template.svg","data":{"lid":"npct_spacer","name":"SPACER","description":"Spacers are those born and bred in the hard vacuum of the endless void. They are adept at maneuvering in and around the difficult, low-g environments found only in space and low orbit – blink and space stations, asteroid fields, and the emptiness between ships in military and commercial fleets.","power":20,"base_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_maneuverable_spacer","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_spacer_systems_spacer","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}],"optional_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_concussion_gun_spacer","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_gravity_rifle_spacer","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_sealant_trap_spacer","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_thumper_grenades_spacer","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}]},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"22FbR6izv7gtceno":3},"flags":{},"_id":"iNAsz00hdZHqmxiV"}
{"name":"ELITE","type":"npc_template","img":"systems/lancer/assets/icons/npc_template.svg","data":{"lid":"npct_elite","name":"ELITE","description":"Elite enemies are tougher and more powerful than most – just a step down from Ultras. They might be especially tough or experienced pilots, special forces, or foes using a higher level of technology or better quality gear than the rank and file. Elites can act several times each round and get additional Structure, which effectively doubles their HP and allows them to make structure damage checks like PCs.","power":100,"base_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_reinforced_elite","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_ready_and_waiting_elite","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_career_soldier_elite","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_specialist_kit_elite","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}],"optional_features":[]},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"22FbR6izv7gtceno":3},"flags":{},"_id":"iQuiCuLZAHKqbuBQ"}
{"name":"EXOTIC","type":"npc_template","img":"systems/lancer/assets/icons/npc_template.svg","data":{"lid":"npct_exotic","name":"EXOTIC","description":"Even in a galaxy of wonders, Exotics are strange and dangerous enemies. Some feature unique technologies not yet available to the wider galaxy or wield archaic weapon styles updated to the modern day, while others carry equipment or adopt tactics that are totally alien to Union doctrine.","power":20,"base_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_xenotech_exotic","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_hardened_target_exotic","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_exotic_systems_exotic","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}],"optional_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_living_chassis_exotic","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_blinkspace_carver_exotic","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_realspace_extrusion_exotic","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_living_weaponry_exotic","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_paracausal_weapon_exotic","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_chronotorus_exotic","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_regenerator_exotic","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}]},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"22FbR6izv7gtceno":3},"flags":{},"_id":"mqnUFxRH7CYozKNU"}
{"name":"VETERAN","type":"npc_template","img":"systems/lancer/assets/icons/npc_template.svg","data":{"lid":"npct_veteran","name":"VETERAN","description":"Veterans are hardened, experienced fighters that have survived several direct engagements. This isn’t their first rodeo, and their ability to withstand morale shocks is far higher than an untested greenhorn. Their value on the field is the experience they bring to a deployment and their steady presence along the line.<br>Use the Veteran template to make more memorable characters.","power":50,"base_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_reinforced_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_veterancy_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_veteran_traits_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"}],"optional_features":[{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_acrobat_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_deadly_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_feign_death_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_hacker_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_hardened_target_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_headshot_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_insulated_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_legendary_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_lesser_sight_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_lightning_reflexes_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_limitless_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_name":"comp_core"},{"id":"","fallback_lid":"npcf_nhp_co_pilot_veteran","type":"npc_feature","reg_n